<p><strong className="hl">Rain, Heavy:</strong> Heavy rain reduces visibility to one-quarter of the normal range, resulting in a -6 penalty on Perception checks. Heavy rain automatically extinguishes unprotected flames and imposes a -6 penalty on ranged attacks.</p>
